<tr>
  <td>
    <b><font face="arial" color="#003399">&quot;Timing attack&quot; protection module</font></b>
    <br />
    <font size="-1">[<i>10/Nov/2004</i>]</font>
    <blockquote><font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1">
      <p>The ProFTPD Project team has developed a <code>mod_delay</code>
